<td colspan=3 class=black><br><p><font class=b>How to play</font><br>
Use the CURSOR KEYS to move Sam around. When not moving, you can press the SPACE BAR to fire your Electro-Spear and stun your enemies. Keep stunning them for long enough, and they'll give up the ghost! You can also kill enemies with rocks: tunnel underneath them and try to squash your enemies as they fall. Don't let the enemies touch you, and watch out for the dragons' fireballs.<br><br>
Sam gets an extra life for every 25000 points he scores - collect the bonus gems, coins and treasure chests for extra points.<br><br>

Dig for victory!<br><br>
<font class=b>Tips:</font><br>
- Try to collect as much treasure as possible to get the bonus extra lives.<br>
- Near the level end, enemies escape top left so try and clear this area first.<br>
- Press S to turn the sound effects on and off and M to turn the music on and off.<br>
- Press P to toggle the game pause.<br><br>






















































